window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Returning to Haven after freeing Alessa's mother, Oberon and Alessa work to grow their strength and forces in the shadows of the desert. Their string of destruction does not go unnoticed though, and the Lordships gather their own forces to protect themselves from the undead that appears to be spreading like wildfire in the west. The only question is, will they be enough to stop the force of nature known as Oberon?</p>"; 
